text: Freode huna æt ocmund tune on mides sumeres messe æuen for þon.
And for þa.
On feower wegas on brunes gewitnesse messepreostes & on ealra þæra preosta.
Birhtric freode hroda æt curi tune on sunnan dæge ofer pentecostenes messe daig on.
Preosta.
Ealra þara hyred preosta & on.
Þys sint þara manna naman ðe man freode for ordgar æt bradan stane ða he læg on adle.

Þæt ys cynsie fram liwtune & godcild of lamburnan & leofric of swuran tune dola wines sunu & eadsige of cyric forda & ælfgyþ of boc lande & smala of ocmund tune & wifman of brada stane & byrhflæd of tref meu tune & ælflæd of clymes tune.
On wynstanes gewytnysse mæsse preostæs & on wulfsies æt lamburnan & on eallra þara hired preosta.
& ælfgyð of swuran tune & þær his to gewitnysse cynsie preost and goda preost, & ælfric preost, ðe þis ge wryt wrat.
Þis was æt borslea gedon for ordgar.
Eadgifu gefreode ælfgiðe birhsies dohtor hlaf bryttan æt borslea on feower wegas.
On wynstanes gewittnesse mæssepreostes, & on goda preostes, & on cynstanes goda suna, & on afan.
Birhtric gefreode æffan æt curritune on brunes gewitnesse mæssepreostes, & on wynstanes preostes, & on ealra þæra hyred preosta.
Eadgyfu gefreode leofrune æt curritune for ordgar on brunes gewittnesse messe preostes & on ealra þæra hyred preosta.
Byrhtric gefreode ribrost & hwite on middes wintres mæsse dæg æt tiwarhel on prudes gewitnysse mæsse preostes.
Eadgyfu gefreode wulfric on feower wegas þrim ucan ær middan sumera.
On gewittnesse byrhstanes mæsse preostes, & on cynstanes & on clerices þe þis gewrat.
Eadgyfu gefreode wulfwunne on middes sumeres mæsse dæg on wulfnoþes gewitnysse mæsse preostes & on ealra þæra hired preosta.
Eadgyfu gefreode æþelgyfe wuncildes wif on feower wegas on middes sumeres mæsse æfen æt bræg.
On brunes gewittnisse mæsse preostes & on wulfnoðes mæsse preostes & on eallra þæra hyred preosta.
